data.description: Nestled at the end of a cul-de-sac, this split-level home features a multi-level floorplan with updated luxury vinyl flooring. This home features an attached oversize two car garage with a garage door opener. The garage connects to the home through a spacious three-season room that offers space for endless possibilities and room for expanded living area. Entering into the home a large laundry/ utility room is your gateway into an updated modern kitchen that features a newer gas range, built in microwave, updated cabinetry, and luxury vinyl flooring. The kitchen opens to a unique dining/ gathering area with a full brick wall decorative fireplace. A large picture window offers a view of the private back yard. First floor living room offers natural light and view of the front yard. The first-floor bedroom offers a convent sleeping area. The second floor of the home features two good sized bedrooms and an updated full bath. New furance/AC, upated bathroom.
